test -f /opt/Axodus/AxodusAPP/.instructions/STATUS.md || true
test -f /opt/Axodus/Dex/.instructions/STATUS.md || true
test -f /opt/Axodus/Core/.instructions/STATUS.md || true
test -f /opt/Axodus/BBA-Agency/.instructions/STATUS.md || true
```

Result: PASS.

Nucleus documentation diff checks were run:

```bash
for d in Core Governance AxodusAPP Defi BBA-Agency; do
  git -C "/opt/Axodus/$d" diff --check -- .instructions/STATUS.md
done
```

Result: PASS.

Root git check:

```bash
git status --short --branch
```

Result: FAIL as expected; `/opt/Axodus` is not a Git repository.

